former President Ronald Reagan during the second session of the
Republican National Convention, Tuesday. (Chang W. Lee/The New York
Times)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT30) PHILADELPHIA -- Aug. 1, 2000 -- GOP-RDP-9 -- Dick
