Love," written on a street in Arta, in reference to a conference
nearby attended by Somalis on the establishment of a government in
Somalia. (Tyler Hicks/The New York Times)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT6) CANTON, Ohio -- Aug. 1, 2000 -- TV-SPORTS-COLUMN-BOS
--  Not in recent memory has there been more hype surrounding a
broadcaster than the ado about Dennis Miller, who debuted as a
commentator on ABC's "Monday Night Football" this week. Miller, in
the ABC broadcast booth, pumps his fist to fans on Monday. (Matthew
J. Lee/The Boston Globe)
</P>
