<HEADER>
A2456 &Cx1f; var-z
u i BC-R-BOSNIA-MASSACRES-RE     08-02 0420
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-BOSNIA-MASSACRES-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
IN A PICTURE BOOK, CLUES TO A MASSACRE 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
 By STEVEN ERLANGER   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
