<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-02 11:01 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0396 &Cx1f; tad-z
r a BC-NEWS-QUESTIONS03-FILE     08-02 1306
