   NUTSNBOLTS _ There seemed to be fireplace inserts and wood
stoves everywhere during the 1970s and 1980s. More recently
high-tech gas fireplaces seem to be dominant. This week we answer a
question from a family that has gotten rid of its old fireplace
insert. (Cummings, Dayton Daily News). 27. MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   GARDENING-LIFE _ Orchids really have a hold on me. It's been a
while since I've been in an orchid period, about five or six years.
Like many orchid dabblers, I'd enjoy the blooms for months and then
I'd watch the plants just sit there for the next year or so. Now, I
have returned to orchids with zeal, if not skill. So go the rhythms
of gardening. Ylip to your bookbag or wear around your neck.
(Morrow, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). WITH PHOTOS and LAYOUT.
