<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-02 19:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0881 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r l BC-SWEAT-SAVVY-TEX     08-02 1277
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SWEAT-SAVVY-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
SOPPING WET? GOOD!
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
 By JESSIE MILLIGAN 
