<P>
   GOP-GORTON (Philadelphia) _ For a successful politician, Sen.
Slade Gorton has an unusual aversion to national conventions,
sacred political ground where backs are slapped, smiles are wide
and contributors are especially generous. But even Gorton had to
relent this year. When he arrived here yesterday, Washington
state's senior senator joined his first Republican National
Convention since 1984.
