<P>
   WILLEY-COLUMN (Philadelphia) - It hasn't been easy for Sen. John
McCain at the Republican National Convention this week. Every now
and then, like the Dennis the Menace who just couldn't control his
mischief, McCain let slip glimpses of the struggle behind the
fagade. By KEVEN ANN WILLEY. Story will move in the ``K'' category.
