</P>
<P>
   &UR; ``Classy, sexy, feminine _ those are the things I look for in &LR; 
 &UR; clothes. I don't like anything that looks cheap. I don't go for &LR; 
 &UR; overtly sexual things. I like things that leave something to the &LR; 
 &UR; imagination.'' &LR;  -- &LR;   &UR; Jennifer Lopez &LR; , whose low-cut dress left a
molecule to the imagination at the Grammys, in Playboy magazine.
</P>
