Convention from the New York Times News Service as of 9:00 p.m.,
EDT. Additional photos will move within the hour.
</P>
<P>
   (NYT39) PHILADELPHIA -- Aug. 2, 2000 -- GOP-RDP-5 -- Wednesday
evening's session of the Republican National Convention got
underway when pro football quarterback Steve Young, of the San
Francisco 49ers, delivered the invocation. (Dede Smith/The
Gaineville Sun)
</P>
