<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT20000802.0485 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-02 22:48 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1107 &Cx1f; tad-z
u p BC-GASENATE-QUALIFY0803-     08-02 0483
